<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا ابْنُ نُمَيْرٍ، عَنْ سَعِيدِ بْنِ سِنَانٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> عَنِ الضَّحَّاكِ فِي قَوْلِهِ عَزَّ وَجَلَّ:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{وَلِمَنْ دَخَلَ بَيْتِيَ مُؤْمِنًا}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[نوح: ٢٨]</span> .<span style="color:#006d98"> قَالَ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَسْجِدِي»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>